description: List of plants by common name

plants.name: Banana
plants.species: mainly Musa × paradisica, but also other Musa species and hybrids

plants.name: Bittercress
plants.species: Barbarea vulgaris, Cardamine bulbosa, Cardamine hirsuta

plants.name: Bitterweed
plants.species: Any plant in the Ambrosia genus, specially Ambrosia artemisiifolia, Artemisia trifida, Helenium amarum

plants.name: Blackberry
plants.species: Rubus spp., Rubus pensilvanicus, Rubus occidentalis

plants.name: Juniper
plants.species: Various species in the genus Juniperus

plants.name: Sugar maple
plants.species: Acer saccharum (main use), Acer barbatum, Acer leucoderme,

plants.name: Touch-me-not
plants.species: Impatiens capensis, Impatiens pallida, Mimosa pudica, Cardamine hirsuta
